cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the privacy-preserving outsourcing of network functions, which involves both cryptography and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also proposes instantiations using encryption techniques, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
